author: Anna Salleh
title: Coronavirus doesn't kill many people - but here's how it can
description: Some people, especially those in vulnerable populations are at risk of having severe symptoms from COVID-19 or even dying. How does this happen?
content:
Chances are if you get sick from the latest coronavirus you'll get a pretty mild illness.
